<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <base href="/">
    <title>Class Point</title>
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.1/normalize.min.css"> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.rawgit.com/mfd/09b70eb47474836f25a21660282ce0fd/raw/e06a670afcb2b861ed2ac4a1ef752d062ef6b46b/Gilroy.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.13.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <%- include ('../partials/navbar'); %>
</header>

<main>
    <div class="title1__container m-b-xl">
        <h1 class="title title-1">Class Point</h1>
        <div class="rectangle"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="info__paragraph">
        <p>
            This site is dedicated to helping teachers keep track of classroom points for games, as well as tracking student participation.
        </p>
        <p>
            After signing up you can save a class either by entering students manually or downloading a csv file.
        </p>
        <p>
            Once your class is saved you can play <span>Individual Games</span>, where students compete against each other,
            <span>Boy Vs Girl games,</span> or <span>Team Games,</span> where you can split your class into as many teams as you need. 
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta__container m-b-xl">
        <ul class="navbar__links">
            <% if(currentUser){ %>
                <li class="cta__button"><a href="/classroom">Classes</a></li>
            <% }  else { %>
                <li class="cta__button"><a href="/users/login">Login</a></li>
                <li class="cta__button"><a href="/users/">SignUp</a></li>
            <% } %>    
            
        </ul>
    </div>

    
</main>
<footer>
    <p>class point by Nick de Waal, copyright &#169 2020 all rights reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>